data.description: Look no further, your perfect family home is right here. This home is beautiful inside out with a spacious yard including a Thompson water sealed fence along with a covered back patio. This home has been freshly repainted inside and out, newly installed XL stainless sink for all of your washing needs, all walls in the home have been insulated to help with temperature and sound control, custom frameless shower along with a stone shower pan to finish it off plus much more. This house is a perfect single family home zoned to the prestigious Barbers Hill School district. This home will not disappoint, please come and see for yourself.
